title: Invertebrate Zoology
description: An examination of invertebrates and their habitats. Lecture format.

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): BIOL 20A, BIOE 20B, and BIOE 20C and satisfaction of the Entry Level Writing and Composition requirements. Must be taken concurrently with BIOE 122L.

class_notes: Concurrent Enrollment in BIOE 122L is required.
